`+` (operator-without-parentheses.wipple:1:8-1:9) (error-instance)

  Missing parentheses around the inputs to `+`.
  
  Spaces group before operators do, so you need to put parentheses around just
  the inputs to `+`.
  
  -  `+` (operator-without-parentheses.wipple:1:8-1:9) requires `Add` `()` `Number` (operator-without-parentheses.wipple:1:10-1:11) `_`.
